Document: SpringBoneCollisionCapsule3D
Path: godot/classes/class_springbonecollisioncapsule3d.rst
Summary: Defines properties for configuring a 3D capsule collision shape used in spring bone systems.

- height (float): Vertical size of the capsule. Default: 0.5
- inside (bool): Whether the collision shape is solid (true) or hollow (false). Default: false
- mid_height (float): Vertical position of the capsule's midpoint
- radius (float): Horizontal radius of the capsule. Default: 0.1
